    caption: [Dilation and constriction of the pupil. In dim light, the radially arranged smooth muscle fibers are stimulated to contract by sympathetic neurons, dilating the pupil. In bright light, the circularly arranged smooth muscle fibers are stimulated to contract by parasympathetic neurons, constricting the pupil.],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
