    caption: [A view of the retina as seen with an ophthalmoscope. (a) A photograph and (b) an illustration of the optic fundus (back of the eye). Optic nerve fibers leave the eyeball at the optic disc to form the optic nerve. (Note the blood vessels that can be seen entering the eyeball at the optic disc.)],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
